  "detailed_description": "You wake up in a daze in a small village and can't remember anything.<br />\r\nA penguin called Otto tells you that he found you during a snowstorm.<br />\r\nHe was afraid that you wouldn't survive. You learn that many of the penguins are ill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey tell you about the mysterious disease called freezing fever. You want to help the penguins make a healing potion to make the sick penguins healthy again. But to do this, you need 4 different herbs that grow on distant lands.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut where are these lands?<br />\r\nAnd how do you get there?<br />\r\nYou find out that one of these herbs, called frost blossom, only grows here in the cold snowy landscape. But the penguins don't know exactly where it grows.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou set off in search of other settlements to find out if they know the place where the herb you need can be found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd that's where your adventure begins ...",
  "about_the_game": "You wake up in a daze in a small village and can't remember anything.<br />\r\nA penguin called Otto tells you that he found you during a snowstorm.<br />\r\nHe was afraid that you wouldn't survive. You learn that many of the penguins are ill.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThey tell you about the mysterious disease called freezing fever. You want to help the penguins make a healing potion to make the sick penguins healthy again. But to do this, you need 4 different herbs that grow on distant lands.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nBut where are these lands?<br />\r\nAnd how do you get there?<br />\r\nYou find out that one of these herbs, called frost blossom, only grows here in the cold snowy landscape. But the penguins don't know exactly where it grows.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou set off in search of other settlements to find out if they know the place where the herb you need can be found.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nAnd that's where your adventure begins ...",
